column5: 8 hours & 270 Km later, 7 of the 10 School Salmon Hatcheries were set up by Myself & Mike Blumhagen & the other 3 were set up by Al Wilkins LHFC Past President, Schools from Goderich, Brookside, Wingham x 2, Teeswater x2, Walkerton, Kincardine x2 & Port Elgin are now part of the Libro Financial Group & Lake Huron Fishing Clubs School Salmon Hatchery Program, Enjoy Tight Lines SBK  Eggs were Delivered Today Video
Cool and I wish you all the best of luck!
